  akshan: {"diff":"TRICKY","tone":"#ff8b3d","tldr":"Weather the poke — charge Q on the Heroic Swing cooldown and out-HP the lane.","breakdown":"Akshan plays around Heroic Swing. Hide the Q charge behind the wave, E-slow into the full knockup when Heroic Swing is down, and W + HP stacking makes you unkillable. Doran’s Shield blunts the poke war.","dos":["Charge Q in fog / brush angles","E-shred his step-up","W-shield to trade for free"],"donts":["Channel Q in the open","Waste W shield-burst early","Die without zombie value"],"key":{"slot":"E","name":"Heroic Swing","cd":"14s","note":"His dash + camera swing escape. Engage when it's down.","winT":"SWING DOWN","winS":"Charged Q + E shred."},"win":"Charge Q on the Heroic Swing cooldown and out-HP the lane."},
